{"tid":1147910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【嗅覺挑戰】《氣味展超》台灣登場 腳臭味臭狐味應有盡有","createTime":"2019-05-10T06:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T06:23:45.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dad33682801ffa034c63a22d578807ef23ca9c3b","tid":1147910,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190510/_2019051014170613960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190510%2F_2019051014170613960.jpg&h=c75c927e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">《氣味展超》首次移師海外，在台灣開展。網圖</span><br />\n<br />\n在日本曾吸引20萬人入場的《氣味展超》首次移師海外，在台灣開展！展覽集結50種氣味，由「麝香」到「腳臭味」應有盡有，讓入場人士體驗各種新奇味道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190510/_2019051014170793825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190510%2F_2019051014170793825.jpg&h=e6080953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190510/_2019051014170849553.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190510%2F_2019051014170849553.jpg&h=ea886af2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轟動全日本《氣味展超》是由MCIPHOLDINGS、株式會社PARCO與TV愛知株式會社共同舉辦，自2016年起在日本國內七大都市舉辦巡迴展覽，共吸引逾20萬人次入場。<br />\n<br />\n展覽集結世界上50種香味、臭味、食物味，甚至體味，包括被稱為世界上氣味最強烈的「瑞典鹽醃鯡魚」、「臭狐味」、｢臭腳味」、等，亦會有經常用於香水的「白檀味」、各式花香香水等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190510/_2019051014170736067.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190510%2F_2019051014170736067.jpg&h=71765bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190510/_2019051014170992275.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190510%2F_2019051014170992275.jpg&h=80d50fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n展覽今次於4月12日至6月2日期間，在台北「華山1914文化創意產業園區」展開，除了「極致的氣味」，現場更設有能檢測自己氣味的「氣味鑑定器」，即將去台灣而又有興趣的朋友，不妨入場體驗「新世界」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190510/_2019051014170922966.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190510%2F_2019051014170922966.jpg&h=905343fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190510/_2019051014171089497.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190510%2F_2019051014171089497.jpg&h=a53283b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/997790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F997790&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGpq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=432983c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F997790&h=16e12d86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/997790</a>"}]}